[[Image:Luigi Datome.jpg|200px|thumb|Luigi Datome]]
'''Luigi Datome''' (born [[November 27]], [[1987]] in [[Montebelluna]], [[Italy]]) is an [[Italy|Italian]] [[basketball]] player currently signed with [[Lottomatica Roma]]. 

At 202&nbsp;cm, he plays the [[small forward (basketball)|small forward]] position.

